I'd love to see a type of Mail Box feature.They had one way back in Meridian59.Just a private little message pick-up area that you could access,where others could leave a 'brief' message for you while you were not in EQ.
Such as guild/raid/quest info.

I used to love getting on the game and seeing the "You've got mail!" message.Friends can keep you up to date on things you missed while away,or important things you should know about as soon as you log on,if they're not on to tell you about them.

This feature would help people keep in contact better that would normally only see eachother every so often due to time zone differences.It would also greatly enhance guilds keeping all members currently up to date on guild happenings.

